name: Weather party bag
description:
* Weather hair pin party bag

* 3 nature inspired hair pins. Handcrafted and stored neatly on a presentation card ready for pinning and clipping as you will. One here, one there and a spare for a friend. Jolly and fun. What's not to love. 

* Mini Kewpie

* Candy rooty toot-toot

* Vintage snap card. Perfect for craft, scrap booking, or just to treasure! 

* Snap card and retro sweetie subject to variations

* All wrapped up in our fabulous signature packaging

* Plenty of tag space for your own personal message
